observations.recommendation:
10.5. We recommended that Management direct the Accounting Office or the
Inventory Committee to
a. mobilize additional competent personnel to facilitate the inventory
of all PPE items;
b. classify properly PPE items;
c. prepare and maintain PPE ledger Cards and Property Ledgers;
d. strengthen the controls on the procedures of PPE handling and
recording by performing a periodic reconcilation between the
records of the accounting office and the actual property and
inventory results.
